    523 <a href="#l504" class="line" id="l504">    504</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l485&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l485&quot;&gt;    485&lt;/a&gt; 	float roughnessToMip( float roughness ) {
    524 <a href="#l505" class="line" id="l505">    505</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l486&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l486&quot;&gt;    486&lt;/a&gt; 		float mip = 0.0;

   1042 <a href="#l1023" class="line" id="l1023">   1023</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1004&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1004&quot;&gt;   1004&lt;/a&gt; vec3 Schlick_to_F0( const in vec3 f, const in float f90, const in float dotVH ) {
   1043 <a href="#l1024" class="line" id="l1024">   1024</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1005&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1005&quot;&gt;   1005&lt;/a&gt;     float x = clamp( 1.0 - dotVH, 0.0, 1.0 );
   1044 <a href="#l1025" class="line" id="l1025">   1025</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1006&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1006&quot;&gt;   1006&lt;/a&gt;     float x2 = x * x;

   1046 <a href="#l1027" class="line" id="l1027">   1027</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1008&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1008&quot;&gt;   1008&lt;/a&gt;     return ( f - vec3( f90 ) * x5 ) / ( 1.0 - x5 );
   1047 <a href="#l1028" class="line" id="l1028">   1028</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1009&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1009&quot;&gt;   1009&lt;/a&gt; }
   1048 <a href="#l1029" class="line" id="l1029">   1029</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1010&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1010&quot;&gt;   1010&lt;/a&gt; float V_GGX_SmithCorrelated( const in float alpha, const in float dotNL, const in float dotNV ) {
   1049 <a href="#l1030" class="line" id="l1030">   1030</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1011&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1011&quot;&gt;   1011&lt;/a&gt; 	float a2 = pow2( alpha );
   1050 <a href="#l1031" class="line" id="l1031">   1031</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1012&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1012&quot;&gt;   1012&lt;/a&gt; 	float gv = dotNL * sqrt( a2 + ( 1.0 - a2 ) * pow2( dotNV ) );

   1053 <a href="#l1034" class="line" id="l1034">   1034</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1015&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1015&quot;&gt;   1015&lt;/a&gt; }
   1054 <a href="#l1035" class="line" id="l1035">   1035</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1016&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1016&quot;&gt;   1016&lt;/a&gt; float D_GGX( const in float alpha, const in float dotNH ) {
   1055 <a href="#l1036" class="line" id="l1036">   1036</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1017&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1017&quot;&gt;   1017&lt;/a&gt; 	float a2 = pow2( alpha );

   1058 <a href="#l1039" class="line" id="l1039">   1039</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1020&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1020&quot;&gt;   1020&lt;/a&gt; }

   1061 <a href="#l1042" class="line" id="l1042">   1042</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1023&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1023&quot;&gt;   1023&lt;/a&gt; 		float gv = dotNL * length( vec3( alphaT * dotTV, alphaB * dotBV, dotNV ) );
   1062 <a href="#l1043" class="line" id="l1043">   1043</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1024&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1024&quot;&gt;   1024&lt;/a&gt; 		float gl = dotNV * length( vec3( alphaT * dotTL, alphaB * dotBL, dotNL ) );

   1134 <a href="#l1115" class="line" id="l1115">   1115</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1096&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1096&quot;&gt;   1096&lt;/a&gt; 	float x = dot( v1, v2 );

   1173 <a href="#l1154" class="line" id="l1154">   1154</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1135&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1135&quot;&gt;   1135&lt;/a&gt; 	float sin2h = max( 1.0 - cos2h, 0.0078125 );
   1174 <a href="#l1155" class="line" id="l1155">   1155</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1136&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1136&quot;&gt;   1136&lt;/a&gt; 	return ( 2.0 + invAlpha ) * pow( sin2h, invAlpha * 0.5 ) / ( 2.0 * PI );
   1175 <a href="#l1156" class="line" id="l1156">   1156</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1137&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1137&quot;&gt;   1137&lt;/a&gt; }
   1176 <a href="#l1157" class="line" id="l1157">   1157</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1138&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1138&quot;&gt;   1138&lt;/a&gt; float V_Neubelt( float dotNV, float dotNL ) {
   1177 <a href="#l1158" class="line" id="l1158">   1158</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1139&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1139&quot;&gt;   1139&lt;/a&gt; 	return saturate( 1.0 / ( 4.0 * ( dotNL + dotNV - dotNL * dotNV ) ) );
   1178 <a href="#l1159" class="line" id="l1159">   1159</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1140&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1140&quot;&gt;   1140&lt;/a&gt; }
   1179 <a href="#l1160" class="line" id="l1160">   1160</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1141&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1141&quot;&gt;   1141&lt;/a&gt; vec3 BRDF_Sheen( const in vec3 lightDir, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, vec3 sheenColor, const in float sheenRoughness ) {
   1180 <a href="#l1161" class="line" id="l1161">   1161</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1142&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1142&quot;&gt;   1142&lt;/a&gt; 	vec3 halfDir = normalize( lightDir + viewDir );
   1181 <a href="#l1162" class="line" id="l1162">   1162</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1143&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1143&quot;&gt;   1143&lt;/a&gt; 	float dotNL = saturate( dot( normal, lightDir ) );
   1182 <a href="#l1163" class="line" id="l1163">   1163</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1144&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1144&quot;&gt;   1144&lt;/a&gt; 	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   1183 <a href="#l1164" class="line" id="l1164">   1164</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1145&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1145&quot;&gt;   1145&lt;/a&gt; 	float dotNH = saturate( dot( normal, halfDir ) );
   1184 <a href="#l1165" class="line" id="l1165">   1165</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1146&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1146&quot;&gt;   1146&lt;/a&gt; 	float D = D_Charlie( sheenRoughness, dotNH );
   1185 <a href="#l1166" class="line" id="l1166">   1166</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1147&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1147&quot;&gt;   1147&lt;/a&gt; 	float V = V_Neubelt( dotNV, dotNL );

   1187 <a href="#l1168" class="line" id="l1168">   1168</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1149&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1149&quot;&gt;   1149&lt;/a&gt; }
   1188 <a href="#l1169" class="line" id="l1169">   1169</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1150&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1150&quot;&gt;   1150&lt;/a&gt; #endif
   1189 <a href="#l1170" class="line" id="l1170">   1170</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1151&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1151&quot;&gt;   1151&lt;/a&gt; float IBLSheenBRDF( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in float roughness ) {
   1190 <a href="#l1171" class="line" id="l1171">   1171</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1152&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1152&quot;&gt;   1152&lt;/a&gt; 	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   1191 <a href="#l1172" class="line" id="l1172">   1172</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1153&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1153&quot;&gt;   1153&lt;/a&gt; 	float r2 = roughness * roughness;
   1192 <a href="#l1173" class="line" id="l1173">   1173</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1154&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1154&quot;&gt;   1154&lt;/a&gt; 	float a = roughness &amp;lt; 0.25 ? -339.2 * r2 + 161.4 * roughness - 25.9 : -8.48 * r2 + 14.3 * roughness - 9.95;
   1193 <a href="#l1174" class="line" id="l1174">   1174</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1155&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1155&quot;&gt;   1155&lt;/a&gt; 	float b = roughness &amp;lt; 0.25 ? 44.0 * r2 - 23.7 * roughness + 3.26 : 1.97 * r2 - 3.27 * roughness + 0.72;
   1194 <a href="#l1175" class="line" id="l1175">   1175</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1156&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1156&quot;&gt;   1156&lt;/a&gt; 	float DG = exp( a * dotNV + b ) + ( roughness &amp;lt; 0.25 ? 0.0 : 0.1 * ( roughness - 0.25 ) );
   1195 <a href="#l1176" class="line" id="l1176">   1176</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1157&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1157&quot;&gt;   1157&lt;/a&gt; 	return saturate( DG * RECIPROCAL_PI );
   1196 <a href="#l1177" class="line" id="l1177">   1177</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1158&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1158&quot;&gt;   1158&lt;/a&gt; }
   1197 <a href="#l1178" class="line" id="l1178">   1178</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1159&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1159&quot;&gt;   1159&lt;/a&gt; vec2 DFGApprox( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in float roughness ) {
   1198 <a href="#l1179" class="line" id="l1179">   1179</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1160&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1160&quot;&gt;   1160&lt;/a&gt; 	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   1199 <a href="#l1180" class="line" id="l1180">   1180</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1161&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1161&quot;&gt;   1161&lt;/a&gt; 	const vec4 c0 = vec4( - 1, - 0.0275, - 0.572, 0.022 );
   1200 <a href="#l1181" class="line" id="l1181">   1181</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1162&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1162&quot;&gt;   1162&lt;/a&gt; 	const vec4 c1 = vec4( 1, 0.0425, 1.04, - 0.04 );
   1201 <a href="#l1182" class="line" id="l1182">   1182</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1163&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1163&quot;&gt;   1163&lt;/a&gt; 	vec4 r = roughness * c0 + c1;
   1202 <a href="#l1183" class="line" id="l1183">   1183</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1164&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1164&quot;&gt;   1164&lt;/a&gt; 	float a004 = min( r.x * r.x, exp2( - 9.28 * dotNV ) ) * r.x + r.y;
   1203 <a href="#l1184" class="line" id="l1184">   1184</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1165&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1165&quot;&gt;   1165&lt;/a&gt; 	vec2 fab = vec2( - 1.04, 1.04 ) * a004 + r.zw;
   1204 <a href="#l1185" class="line" id="l1185">   1185</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1166&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1166&quot;&gt;   1166&lt;/a&gt; 	return fab;
   1205 <a href="#l1186" class="line" id="l1186">   1186</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1167&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1167&quot;&gt;   1167&lt;/a&gt; }
   1206 <a href="#l1187" class="line" id="l1187">   1187</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1168&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1168&quot;&gt;   1168&lt;/a&gt; vec3 EnvironmentBRDF( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in float roughness ) {
   1207 <a href="#l1188" class="line" id="l1188">   1188</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1169&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1169&quot;&gt;   1169&lt;/a&gt; 	vec2 fab = DFGApprox( normal, viewDir, roughness );

   1209 <a href="#l1190" class="line" id="l1190">   1190</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1171&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1171&quot;&gt;   1171&lt;/a&gt; }
   1210 <a href="#l1191" class="line" id="l1191">   1191</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1172&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1172&quot;&gt;   1172&lt;/a&gt; #ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   1211 <a href="#l1192" class="line" id="l1192">   1192</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1173&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1173&quot;&gt;   1173&lt;/a&gt; void computeMultiscatteringIridescence( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in float iridescence, const in vec3 iridescenceF0, const in float roughness, inout vec3 singleScatter, inout vec3 multiScatter ) {
   1212 <a href="#l1193" class="line" id="l1193">   1193</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1174&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1174&quot;&gt;   1174&lt;/a&gt; #else

   1214 <a href="#l1195" class="line" id="l1195">   1195</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1176&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1176&quot;&gt;   1176&lt;/a&gt; #endif

   1217 <a href="#l1198" class="line" id="l1198">   1198</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1179&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1179&quot;&gt;   1179&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 Fr = mix( specularColor, iridescenceF0, iridescence );
   1218 <a href="#l1199" class="line" id="l1199">   1199</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1180&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1180&quot;&gt;   1180&lt;/a&gt; 	#else
   1219 <a href="#l1200" class="line" id="l1200">   1200</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1181&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1181&quot;&gt;   1181&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 Fr = specularColor;
   1220 <a href="#l1201" class="line" id="l1201">   1201</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1182&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1182&quot;&gt;   1182&lt;/a&gt; 	#endif
   1221 <a href="#l1202" class="line" id="l1202">   1202</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1183&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1183&quot;&gt;   1183&lt;/a&gt; 	vec3 FssEss = Fr * fab.x + specularF90 * fab.y;
   1222 <a href="#l1203" class="line" id="l1203">   1203</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1184&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1184&quot;&gt;   1184&lt;/a&gt; 	float Ess = fab.x + fab.y;
   1223 <a href="#l1204" class="line" id="l1204">   1204</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1185&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1185&quot;&gt;   1185&lt;/a&gt; 	float Ems = 1.0 - Ess;
   1224 <a href="#l1205" class="line" id="l1205">   1205</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1186&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1186&quot;&gt;   1186&lt;/a&gt; 	vec3 Favg = Fr + ( 1.0 - Fr ) * 0.047619;	vec3 Fms = FssEss * Favg / ( 1.0 - Ems * Favg );
   1225 <a href="#l1206" class="line" id="l1206">   1206</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1187&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1187&quot;&gt;   1187&lt;/a&gt; 	singleScatter += FssEss;

   1227 <a href="#l1208" class="line" id="l1208">   1208</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1189&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1189&quot;&gt;   1189&lt;/a&gt; }

   1230 <a href="#l1211" class="line" id="l1211">   1211</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1192&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1192&quot;&gt;   1192&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 normal = geometryNormal;

   1248 <a href="#l1229" class="line" id="l1229">   1229</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1210&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1210&quot;&gt;   1210&lt;/a&gt; 			vec3( t1.z, 0, t1.w )
   1249 <a href="#l1230" class="line" id="l1230">   1230</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1211&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1211&quot;&gt;   1211&lt;/a&gt; 		);
   1250 <a href="#l1231" class="line" id="l1231">   1231</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1212&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1212&quot;&gt;   1212&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 fresnel = ( material.specularColor * t2.x + ( vec3( 1.0 ) - material.specularColor ) * t2.y );

   1252 <a href="#l1233" class="line" id="l1233">   1233</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1214&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1214&quot;&gt;   1214&lt;/a&gt; 		reflectedLight.directDiffuse += lightColor * material.diffuseColor * LTC_Evaluate( normal, viewDir, position, mat3( 1.0 ), rectCoords );

   1256 <a href="#l1237" class="line" id="l1237">   1237</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1218&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1218&quot;&gt;   1218&lt;/a&gt; 	float dotNL = saturate( dot( geometryNormal, directLight.direction ) );
   1257 <a href="#l1238" class="line" id="l1238">   1238</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1219&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1219&quot;&gt;   1219&lt;/a&gt; 	vec3 irradiance = dotNL * directLight.color;

   1879 <a href="#l1860" class="line" id="l1860">   1860</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1841&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1841&quot;&gt;   1841&lt;/a&gt; 					 f.y )

   1881 <a href="#l1862" class="line" id="l1862">   1862</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1843&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1843&quot;&gt;   1843&lt;/a&gt; 		#elif defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_VSM )
   1882 <a href="#l1863" class="line" id="l1863">   1863</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1844&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1844&quot;&gt;   1844&lt;/a&gt; 			shadow = VSMShadow( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy, shadowCoord.z );
   1883 <a href="#l1864" class="line" id="l1864">   1864</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1845&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1845&quot;&gt;   1845&lt;/a&gt; 		#else

   1888 <a href="#l1869" class="line" id="l1869">   1869</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1850&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1850&quot;&gt;   1850&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   1889 <a href="#l1870" class="line" id="l1870">   1870</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1851&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1851&quot;&gt;   1851&lt;/a&gt; 	vec2 cubeToUV( vec3 v, float texelSizeY ) {
   1890 <a href="#l1871" class="line" id="l1871">   1871</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1852&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1852&quot;&gt;   1852&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 absV = abs( v );
   1891 <a href="#l1872" class="line" id="l1872">   1872</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1853&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1853&quot;&gt;   1853&lt;/a&gt; 		float scaleToCube = 1.0 / max( absV.x, max( absV.y, absV.z ) );
   1892 <a href="#l1873" class="line" id="l1873">   1873</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1854&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1854&quot;&gt;   1854&lt;/a&gt; 		absV *= scaleToCube;

   1894 <a href="#l1875" class="line" id="l1875">   1875</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1856&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1856&quot;&gt;   1856&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 planar = v.xy;
   1895 <a href="#l1876" class="line" id="l1876">   1876</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1857&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1857&quot;&gt;   1857&lt;/a&gt; 		float almostATexel = 1.5 * texelSizeY;
   1896 <a href="#l1877" class="line" id="l1877">   1877</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1858&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1858&quot;&gt;   1858&lt;/a&gt; 		float almostOne = 1.0 - almostATexel;
   1897 <a href="#l1878" class="line" id="l1878">   1878</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1859&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1859&quot;&gt;   1859&lt;/a&gt; 		if ( absV.z &amp;gt;= almostOne ) {
   1898 <a href="#l1879" class="line" id="l1879">   1879</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1860&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1860&quot;&gt;   1860&lt;/a&gt; 			if ( v.z &amp;gt; 0.0 )
   1899 <a href="#l1880" class="line" id="l1880">   1880</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1861&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1861&quot;&gt;   1861&lt;/a&gt; 				planar.x = 4.0 - v.x;
   1900 <a href="#l1881" class="line" id="l1881">   1881</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1862&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1862&quot;&gt;   1862&lt;/a&gt; 		} else if ( absV.x &amp;gt;= almostOne ) {
   1901 <a href="#l1882" class="line" id="l1882">   1882</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1863&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1863&quot;&gt;   1863&lt;/a&gt; 			float signX = sign( v.x );
   1902 <a href="#l1883" class="line" id="l1883">   1883</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1864&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1864&quot;&gt;   1864&lt;/a&gt; 			planar.x = v.z * signX + 2.0 * signX;
   1903 <a href="#l1884" class="line" id="l1884">   1884</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1865&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1865&quot;&gt;   1865&lt;/a&gt; 		} else if ( absV.y &amp;gt;= almostOne ) {
   1904 <a href="#l1885" class="line" id="l1885">   1885</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1866&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1866&quot;&gt;   1866&lt;/a&gt; 			float signY = sign( v.y );
   1905 <a href="#l1886" class="line" id="l1886">   1886</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1867&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1867&quot;&gt;   1867&lt;/a&gt; 			planar.x = v.x + 2.0 * signY + 2.0;
   1906 <a href="#l1887" class="line" id="l1887">   1887</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1868&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1868&quot;&gt;   1868&lt;/a&gt; 			planar.y = v.z * signY - 2.0;
   1907 <a href="#l1888" class="line" id="l1888">   1888</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1869&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1869&quot;&gt;   1869&lt;/a&gt; 		}
   1908 <a href="#l1889" class="line" id="l1889">   1889</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1870&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1870&quot;&gt;   1870&lt;/a&gt; 		return vec2( 0.125, 0.25 ) * planar + vec2( 0.375, 0.75 );

   1910 <a href="#l1891" class="line" id="l1891">   1891</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1872&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1872&quot;&gt;   1872&lt;/a&gt; 	float getPointShadow( sampler2D shadowMap, vec2 shadowMapSize, float shadowIntensity, float shadowBias, float shadowRadius, vec4 shadowCoord, float shadowCameraNear, float shadowCameraFar ) {
   1911 <a href="#l1892" class="line" id="l1892">   1892</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l1873&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l1873&quot;&gt;   1873&lt;/a&gt; 		float shadow = 1.0;

   2243 <a href="#l2224" class="line" id="l2224">   2224</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2205&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2205&quot;&gt;   2205&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2244 <a href="#l2225" class="line" id="l2225">   2225</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2206&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2206&quot;&gt;   2206&lt;/a&gt; 	float h0( float a ) {
   2245 <a href="#l2226" class="line" id="l2226">   2226</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2207&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2207&quot;&gt;   2207&lt;/a&gt; 		return - 1.0 + w1( a ) / ( w0( a ) + w1( a ) );
   2246 <a href="#l2227" class="line" id="l2227">   2227</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2208&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2208&quot;&gt;   2208&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2247 <a href="#l2228" class="line" id="l2228">   2228</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2209&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2209&quot;&gt;   2209&lt;/a&gt; 	float h1( float a ) {
   2248 <a href="#l2229" class="line" id="l2229">   2229</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2210&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2210&quot;&gt;   2210&lt;/a&gt; 		return 1.0 + w3( a ) / ( w2( a ) + w3( a ) );
   2249 <a href="#l2230" class="line" id="l2230">   2230</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2211&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2211&quot;&gt;   2211&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2250 <a href="#l2231" class="line" id="l2231">   2231</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2212&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2212&quot;&gt;   2212&lt;/a&gt; 	vec4 bicubic( sampler2D tex, vec2 uv, vec4 texelSize, float lod ) {
   2251 <a href="#l2232" class="line" id="l2232">   2232</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2213&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2213&quot;&gt;   2213&lt;/a&gt; 		uv = uv * texelSize.zw + 0.5;

   2255 <a href="#l2236" class="line" id="l2236">   2236</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2217&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2217&quot;&gt;   2217&lt;/a&gt; 		float g1x = g1( fuv.x );
   2256 <a href="#l2237" class="line" id="l2237">   2237</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2218&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2218&quot;&gt;   2218&lt;/a&gt; 		float h0x = h0( fuv.x );
   2257 <a href="#l2238" class="line" id="l2238">   2238</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2219&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2219&quot;&gt;   2219&lt;/a&gt; 		float h1x = h1( fuv.x );
   2258 <a href="#l2239" class="line" id="l2239">   2239</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2220&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2220&quot;&gt;   2220&lt;/a&gt; 		float h0y = h0( fuv.y );
   2259 <a href="#l2240" class="line" id="l2240">   2240</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2221&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2221&quot;&gt;   2221&lt;/a&gt; 		float h1y = h1( fuv.y );
   2260 <a href="#l2241" class="line" id="l2241">   2241</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2222&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2222&quot;&gt;   2222&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 p0 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h0x, iuv.y + h0y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   2261 <a href="#l2242" class="line" id="l2242">   2242</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2223&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2223&quot;&gt;   2223&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 p1 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h1x, iuv.y + h0y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   2262 <a href="#l2243" class="line" id="l2243">   2243</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2224&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2224&quot;&gt;   2224&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 p2 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h0x, iuv.y + h1y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   2263 <a href="#l2244" class="line" id="l2244">   2244</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2225&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2225&quot;&gt;   2225&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 p3 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h1x, iuv.y + h1y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   2264 <a href="#l2245" class="line" id="l2245">   2245</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2226&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2226&quot;&gt;   2226&lt;/a&gt; 		return g0( fuv.y ) * ( g0x * textureLod( tex, p0, lod ) + g1x * textureLod( tex, p1, lod ) ) +
   2265 <a href="#l2246" class="line" id="l2246">   2246</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2227&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2227&quot;&gt;   2227&lt;/a&gt; 			g1( fuv.y ) * ( g0x * textureLod( tex, p2, lod ) + g1x * textureLod( tex, p3, lod ) );
   2266 <a href="#l2247" class="line" id="l2247">   2247</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2228&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2228&quot;&gt;   2228&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2267 <a href="#l2248" class="line" id="l2248">   2248</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2229&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2229&quot;&gt;   2229&lt;/a&gt; 	vec4 textureBicubic( sampler2D sampler, vec2 uv, float lod ) {
   2268 <a href="#l2249" class="line" id="l2249">   2249</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2230&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2230&quot;&gt;   2230&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 fLodSize = vec2( textureSize( sampler, int( lod ) ) );
   2269 <a href="#l2250" class="line" id="l2250">   2250</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2231&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2231&quot;&gt;   2231&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 cLodSize = vec2( textureSize( sampler, int( lod + 1.0 ) ) );
   2270 <a href="#l2251" class="line" id="l2251">   2251</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2232&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2232&quot;&gt;   2232&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 fLodSizeInv = 1.0 / fLodSize;
   2271 <a href="#l2252" class="line" id="l2252">   2252</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2233&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2233&quot;&gt;   2233&lt;/a&gt; 		vec2 cLodSizeInv = 1.0 / cLodSize;
   2272 <a href="#l2253" class="line" id="l2253">   2253</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2234&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2234&quot;&gt;   2234&lt;/a&gt; 		vec4 fSample = bicubic( sampler, uv, vec4( fLodSizeInv, fLodSize ), floor( lod ) );
   2273 <a href="#l2254" class="line" id="l2254">   2254</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2235&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2235&quot;&gt;   2235&lt;/a&gt; 		vec4 cSample = bicubic( sampler, uv, vec4( cLodSizeInv, cLodSize ), ceil( lod ) );
   2274 <a href="#l2255" class="line" id="l2255">   2255</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2236&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2236&quot;&gt;   2236&lt;/a&gt; 		return mix( fSample, cSample, fract( lod ) );
   2275 <a href="#l2256" class="line" id="l2256">   2256</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2237&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2237&quot;&gt;   2237&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2276 <a href="#l2257" class="line" id="l2257">   2257</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2238&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2238&quot;&gt;   2238&lt;/a&gt; 	vec3 getVolumeTransmissionRay( const in vec3 n, const in vec3 v, const in float thickness, const in float ior, const in mat4 modelMatrix ) {
   2277 <a href="#l2258" class="line" id="l2258">   2258</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2239&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2239&quot;&gt;   2239&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 refractionVector = refract( - v, normalize( n ), 1.0 / ior );
   2278 <a href="#l2259" class="line" id="l2259">   2259</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2240&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2240&quot;&gt;   2240&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 modelScale;
   2279 <a href="#l2260" class="line" id="l2260">   2260</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2241&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2241&quot;&gt;   2241&lt;/a&gt; 		modelScale.x = length( vec3( modelMatrix[ 0 ].xyz ) );
   2280 <a href="#l2261" class="line" id="l2261">   2261</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2242&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2242&quot;&gt;   2242&lt;/a&gt; 		modelScale.y = length( vec3( modelMatrix[ 1 ].xyz ) );
   2281 <a href="#l2262" class="line" id="l2262">   2262</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2243&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2243&quot;&gt;   2243&lt;/a&gt; 		modelScale.z = length( vec3( modelMatrix[ 2 ].xyz ) );
   2282 <a href="#l2263" class="line" id="l2263">   2263</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2244&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2244&quot;&gt;   2244&lt;/a&gt; 		return normalize( refractionVector ) * thickness * modelScale;
   2283 <a href="#l2264" class="line" id="l2264">   2264</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2245&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2245&quot;&gt;   2245&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2284 <a href="#l2265" class="line" id="l2265">   2265</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2246&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2246&quot;&gt;   2246&lt;/a&gt; 	float applyIorToRoughness( const in float roughness, const in float ior ) {
   2285 <a href="#l2266" class="line" id="l2266">   2266</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2247&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2247&quot;&gt;   2247&lt;/a&gt; 		return roughness * clamp( ior * 2.0 - 2.0, 0.0, 1.0 );
   2286 <a href="#l2267" class="line" id="l2267">   2267</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2248&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2248&quot;&gt;   2248&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2287 <a href="#l2268" class="line" id="l2268">   2268</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2249&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2249&quot;&gt;   2249&lt;/a&gt; 	vec4 getTransmissionSample( const in vec2 fragCoord, const in float roughness, const in float ior ) {
   2288 <a href="#l2269" class="line" id="l2269">   2269</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2250&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2250&quot;&gt;   2250&lt;/a&gt; 		float lod = log2( transmissionSamplerSize.x ) * applyIorToRoughness( roughness, ior );
   2289 <a href="#l2270" class="line" id="l2270">   2270</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2251&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2251&quot;&gt;   2251&lt;/a&gt; 		return textureBicubic( transmissionSamplerMap, fragCoord.xy, lod );
   2290 <a href="#l2271" class="line" id="l2271">   2271</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2252&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2252&quot;&gt;   2252&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2291 <a href="#l2272" class="line" id="l2272">   2272</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2253&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2253&quot;&gt;   2253&lt;/a&gt; 	vec3 volumeAttenuation( const in float transmissionDistance, const in vec3 attenuationColor, const in float attenuationDistance ) {
   2292 <a href="#l2273" class="line" id="l2273">   2273</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2254&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2254&quot;&gt;   2254&lt;/a&gt; 		if ( isinf( attenuationDistance ) ) {
   2293 <a href="#l2274" class="line" id="l2274">   2274</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2255&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2255&quot;&gt;   2255&lt;/a&gt; 			return vec3( 1.0 );
   2294 <a href="#l2275" class="line" id="l2275">   2275</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2256&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2256&quot;&gt;   2256&lt;/a&gt; 		} else {
   2295 <a href="#l2276" class="line" id="l2276">   2276</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2257&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2257&quot;&gt;   2257&lt;/a&gt; 			vec3 attenuationCoefficient = -log( attenuationColor ) / attenuationDistance;
   2296 <a href="#l2277" class="line" id="l2277">   2277</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2258&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2258&quot;&gt;   2258&lt;/a&gt; 			vec3 transmittance = exp( - attenuationCoefficient * transmissionDistance );			return transmittance;
   2297 <a href="#l2278" class="line" id="l2278">   2278</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2259&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2259&quot;&gt;   2259&lt;/a&gt; 		}
   2298 <a href="#l2279" class="line" id="l2279">   2279</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2260&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2260&quot;&gt;   2260&lt;/a&gt; 	}
   2299 <a href="#l2280" class="line" id="l2280">   2280</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2261&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2261&quot;&gt;   2261&lt;/a&gt; 	vec4 getIBLVolumeRefraction( const in vec3 n, const in vec3 v, const in float roughness, const in vec3 diffuseColor,
   2300 <a href="#l2281" class="line" id="l2281">   2281</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2262&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2262&quot;&gt;   2262&lt;/a&gt; 		const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in vec3 position, const in mat4 modelMatrix,
   2301 <a href="#l2282" class="line" id="l2282">   2282</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2263&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2263&quot;&gt;   2263&lt;/a&gt; 		const in mat4 viewMatrix, const in mat4 projMatrix, const in float dispersion, const in float ior, const in float thickness,
   2302 <a href="#l2283" class="line" id="l2283">   2283</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2264&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2264&quot;&gt;   2264&lt;/a&gt; 		const in vec3 attenuationColor, const in float attenuationDistance ) {
   2303 <a href="#l2284" class="line" id="l2284">   2284</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2265&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2265&quot;&gt;   2265&lt;/a&gt; 		vec4 transmittedLight;
   2304 <a href="#l2285" class="line" id="l2285">   2285</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2266&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2266&quot;&gt;   2266&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 transmittance;
   2305 <a href="#l2286" class="line" id="l2286">   2286</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2267&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2267&quot;&gt;   2267&lt;/a&gt; 		#ifdef USE_DISPERSION
   2306 <a href="#l2287" class="line" id="l2287">   2287</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2268&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2268&quot;&gt;   2268&lt;/a&gt; 			float halfSpread = ( ior - 1.0 ) * 0.025 * dispersion;
   2307 <a href="#l2288" class="line" id="l2288">   2288</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2269&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2269&quot;&gt;   2269&lt;/a&gt; 			vec3 iors = vec3( ior - halfSpread, ior, ior + halfSpread );
   2308 <a href="#l2289" class="line" id="l2289">   2289</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2270&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2270&quot;&gt;   2270&lt;/a&gt; 			for ( int i = 0; i &amp;lt; 3; i ++ ) {
   2309 <a href="#l2290" class="line" id="l2290">   2290</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2271&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2271&quot;&gt;   2271&lt;/a&gt; 				vec3 transmissionRay = getVolumeTransmissionRay( n, v, thickness, iors[ i ], modelMatrix );

   2312 <a href="#l2293" class="line" id="l2293">   2293</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2274&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2274&quot;&gt;   2274&lt;/a&gt; 				vec2 refractionCoords = ndcPos.xy / ndcPos.w;
   2313 <a href="#l2294" class="line" id="l2294">   2294</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2275&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2275&quot;&gt;   2275&lt;/a&gt; 				refractionCoords += 1.0;
   2314 <a href="#l2295" class="line" id="l2295">   2295</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2276&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2276&quot;&gt;   2276&lt;/a&gt; 				refractionCoords /= 2.0;
   2315 <a href="#l2296" class="line" id="l2296">   2296</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2277&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2277&quot;&gt;   2277&lt;/a&gt; 				vec4 transmissionSample = getTransmissionSample( refractionCoords, roughness, iors[ i ] );
   2316 <a href="#l2297" class="line" id="l2297">   2297</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2278&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2278&quot;&gt;   2278&lt;/a&gt; 				transmittedLight[ i ] = transmissionSample[ i ];
   2317 <a href="#l2298" class="line" id="l2298">   2298</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2279&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2279&quot;&gt;   2279&lt;/a&gt; 				transmittedLight.a += transmissionSample.a;
   2318 <a href="#l2299" class="line" id="l2299">   2299</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2280&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2280&quot;&gt;   2280&lt;/a&gt; 				transmittance[ i ] = diffuseColor[ i ] * volumeAttenuation( length( transmissionRay ), attenuationColor, attenuationDistance )[ i ];
   2319 <a href="#l2300" class="line" id="l2300">   2300</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2281&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2281&quot;&gt;   2281&lt;/a&gt; 			}

   2321 <a href="#l2302" class="line" id="l2302">   2302</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2283&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2283&quot;&gt;   2283&lt;/a&gt; 		#else
   2322 <a href="#l2303" class="line" id="l2303">   2303</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2284&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2284&quot;&gt;   2284&lt;/a&gt; 			vec3 transmissionRay = getVolumeTransmissionRay( n, v, thickness, ior, modelMatrix );
   2323 <a href="#l2304" class="line" id="l2304">   2304</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2285&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2285&quot;&gt;   2285&lt;/a&gt; 			vec3 refractedRayExit = position + transmissionRay;
   2324 <a href="#l2305" class="line" id="l2305">   2305</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2286&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2286&quot;&gt;   2286&lt;/a&gt; 			vec4 ndcPos = projMatrix * viewMatrix * vec4( refractedRayExit, 1.0 );
   2325 <a href="#l2306" class="line" id="l2306">   2306</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2287&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2287&quot;&gt;   2287&lt;/a&gt; 			vec2 refractionCoords = ndcPos.xy / ndcPos.w;
   2326 <a href="#l2307" class="line" id="l2307">   2307</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2288&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2288&quot;&gt;   2288&lt;/a&gt; 			refractionCoords += 1.0;
   2327 <a href="#l2308" class="line" id="l2308">   2308</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2289&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2289&quot;&gt;   2289&lt;/a&gt; 			refractionCoords /= 2.0;
   2328 <a href="#l2309" class="line" id="l2309">   2309</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2290&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2290&quot;&gt;   2290&lt;/a&gt; 			transmittedLight = getTransmissionSample( refractionCoords, roughness, ior );
   2329 <a href="#l2310" class="line" id="l2310">   2310</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2291&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2291&quot;&gt;   2291&lt;/a&gt; 			transmittance = diffuseColor * volumeAttenuation( length( transmissionRay ), attenuationColor, attenuationDistance );
   2330 <a href="#l2311" class="line" id="l2311">   2311</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2292&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2292&quot;&gt;   2292&lt;/a&gt; 		#endif
   2331 <a href="#l2312" class="line" id="l2312">   2312</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2293&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2293&quot;&gt;   2293&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 attenuatedColor = transmittance * transmittedLight.rgb;
   2332 <a href="#l2313" class="line" id="l2313">   2313</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2294&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2294&quot;&gt;   2294&lt;/a&gt; 		vec3 F = EnvironmentBRDF( n, v, specularColor, specularF90, roughness );
   2333 <a href="#l2314" class="line" id="l2314">   2314</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2295&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2295&quot;&gt;   2295&lt;/a&gt; 		float transmittanceFactor = ( transmittance.r + transmittance.g + transmittance.b ) / 3.0;
   2334 <a href="#l2315" class="line" id="l2315">   2315</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2296&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2296&quot;&gt;   2296&lt;/a&gt; 		return vec4( ( 1.0 - F ) * attenuatedColor, 1.0 - ( 1.0 - transmittedLight.a ) * transmittanceFactor );
   2335 <a href="#l2316" class="line" id="l2316">   2316</a> &lt;a href=&quot;#l2297&quot; class=&quot;line&quot; id=&quot;l2297&quot;&gt;   2297&lt;/a&gt; 	}
